TITLE: Return on When Statement in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to return a value from a `when` statement in Kotlin. The `when` statement can be used as an expression that returns a value.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jetbrains/kotlin-web-site/blob/master/docs/topics/idioms.md#_snippet_23

