TITLE: Generic Parent Finder Using Reified Type Parameter in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: Defines an inline extension function for tree traversal that uses a reified type parameter, allowing direct use of 'is' without runtime reflection. The function is inlined, so type information is preserved at the call site. Returns the matching parent or null, and is called as 'findParentOfType<MyType>()'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jetbrains/kotlin-web-site/blob/master/docs/topics/inline-functions.md#2025-04-22_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
inline fun <reified T> TreeNode.findParentOfType(): T? {
    var p = parent
    while (p != null && p !is T) {
        p = p.parent
    }
    return p as T?
}
```

