TITLE: Kotlin function composition
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates function composition using callable references. The `compose` function combines two functions `f` and `g` into a new function `f(g(x))`. This is applied to `isOdd` and `length` to filter a list of strings based on odd lengths.
