TITLE: Analyze Actor Data: GroupBy, Count, Sort in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates data analysis operations using the Kotlin DataFrame library to find the top 20 most common actor first names. It groups the data by first name, counts the occurrences of each name, sorts the counts in descending order, and takes the top 20 results. Requires an `actorDf` DataFrame.
