TITLE: Encoding AP/Javac Options for kapt CLI
DESCRIPTION: Kotlin function that encodes annotation processor options as a Base64 string for the kapt CLI.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jetbrains/kotlin-web-site/blob/master/docs/topics/kapt.md#2025-04-22_snippet_27

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
fun encodeList(options: Map<String, String>): String {
    val os = ByteArrayOutputStream()
    val oos = ObjectOutputStream(os)

    oos.writeInt(options.size)
    for ((key, value) in options.entries) {
        oos.writeUTF(key)
        oos.writeUTF(value)
    }

    oos.flush()
    return Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(os.toByteArray())
}
```

