TITLE: While Loop Refactoring Exercise in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates a refactored version of the pizza slices counting program using a `while` loop in Kotlin. It initializes `pizzaSlices` to 0 and increments it within the while loop until it reaches 7, printing a message for each slice. Finally, it prints a completion message.
