SOURCE: https://github.com/jetbrains/kotlin-web-site/blob/master/docs/topics/tour/kotlin-tour-control-flow.md#_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
fun main() {
    val words = listOf("dinosaur", "limousine", "magazine", "language")
    for (w in words) {
        if (w.startsWith("l"))
            println(w)
    }
}
```

