TITLE: Demonstrating Expected and Actual Declarations for Multiplatform Projects in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the expected/actual declaration pattern used in Kotlin multiplatform projects. It shows how to define an API in common code with 'expect' keyword and implement it with 'actual' keyword in platform-specific code.
