TITLE: Loop-Based Fixpoint Calculation in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: This code provides an iterative equivalent of the tail recursive version for calculating the fixpoint. It uses a `while` loop instead of recursion. Dependencies include Kotlin's Math.cos function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jetbrains/kotlin-web-site/blob/master/docs/topics/functions.md#2025-04-22_snippet_30

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
val eps = 1E-10 // "good enough", could be 10^-15

private fun findFixPoint(): Double {
    var x = 1.0
    while (true) {
        val y = Math.cos(x)
        if (Math.abs(x - y) < eps) return x
        x = Math.cos(x)
    }
}
```

