TITLE: Building Lazy Sequences with Coroutines in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create lazily generated sequences using coroutines with the yield and yieldAll functions. The sequence generates squares of numbers 1-5 followed by a range of numbers 26-28.
